This directory is reserved for optional parity recordings on a junkyard
Toyota Etios — e.g. swapping in a known-bad ECT sensor on the donor car
to capture an Etios-side ground-truth fault signature for the paper's
cross-vehicle section. Empty in this commit; population is contingent on
finding a donor Etios.

Filename convention follows data/real_faults/README.md, with `etios_`
prefix instead of `skoda_`.
